flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "E2D4114340DCCF447A9A13A4D50851AA", "The tower at Briarmoor is responsible for handling the command out to the guards posted further down the roads leading out of the gateway. As more deserters flock to the highwaymen outposts, they take resources with them to the garrison. The Kaelar officials, swamped as they are, recruit more of the newly arrived to join them at the central farm. As long as there\'s proof of heroics, they\'ll have no choice but to listen. A thick stack of insignias should do the trick. ")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "6F5E9BE94CB407E347A0E79EE87B0332", "Vouch for your merits as a soldier. ")
name: CSQ_0024_ReportOnThornmarch
